cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for 3D human pose estimation, which is a common topic in the computer vision community. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a consensus-based optimization algorithm, which involves optimization techniques and could be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel approach for 3D human pose estimation, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper uses datasets and reports results, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
